title: Luxury Living 3 BEDROOM In Midtown Miami!
posting_body: ['Listing ID 5656165', 'This apartment located in a rental community in Midtown features studio, one, two and three bedroom floor plans,', 'a fully equipped kitchen with stainless steel appliances, Italian cabinetry, LED lighting, smart thermostats, a dishwasher, a balcony,', 'porcelain tile flooring, a living room and a dining room.', 'Enjoy the comforts of elevators, central A/C, in-unit laundry and off-street parking.', 'The community offers a dog wash station, rentable private offices, conference room, catering pantry and kitchen, golf simulator, maker space for bike repair and woodworking,', 'a resident bar and lounge, theater wall, bowling alley, game room, pool with a sundeck, volleyball court, bocce ball, and a fitness center.', 'This community is also wheelchair accessible, deleaded and pet friendly.', 'Located within a five minute drive to the I-195 and Wynwood Walls.', 'LISTING ID 5656165', '*PLEASE REFERENCE ABOVE LISTING ID', 'WHEN INQUIRING*', 'Stop searching.', 'You’ve already come to the right place.', 'If you’re looking for ANY type of property whether it’s a studio, an apartment, a townhouse or single family home...', 'YES WE GOT IT.', 'We’re a ONE STOP shop that can assist you in taking the next step towards your next home today.', 'No one makes it this easy!', 'Just send us a text to', 'show contact info', 'with your name and we can send you a CUSTOM list of properties that match what you’re looking for and get the process started.', 'Thank you!', 'Hannah Edwards', '*DISCLAIMER - We do post properties for a 30 day period of time.', 'Due to High Rental Demand, some properties advertised may be withdrawn, cancelled, rented, pending or sold within the past 30 days.', 'All information is deemed to be correct, but not guaranteed*']
